How can you modify the given input to generate a sentence that incorporates the phrase ‘the sweet smell of success’ in a natural and effective way? Here is the input data in JSON format:
{
  "business": "my new business venture",
  "duration": "months",
  "effort": "hard work"
}
And here is a sample code snippet to generate the desired sentence:
const { business, duration, effort } = inputData;
const sentence = `After ${duration} of ${effort}, ${business} has finally taken off, and I can smell the sweet scent of success.`;
console.log(sentence);

To incorporate the phrase "the sweet smell of success" naturally and effectively into the sentence, you can slightly modify the sentence structure. Here's an updated version of the code snippet:

```javascript
const inputData = {
  business: "my new business venture",
  duration: "months",
  effort: "hard work"
};

const { business, duration, effort } = inputData;
const sentence = `After ${duration} of ${effort}, ${business} has finally taken off, and I can experience the sweet smell of success.`;
console.log(sentence);
```

This version maintains the natural flow while directly incorporating the phrase "the sweet smell of success."
